Package com.thesonofthom.maps

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BmpHeaderMap
    Map to easily parse the BMP file format used by Windows.
    BmpHeaderMap.BitmapFileHeader
    Map to parse the header of a potential BMP file to determine if it is, in fact, a bitmap
    PngFileMap
    Map to easily parse the PNG file format.
    PngFileMap.PngHeader
    Map to parse the header of a potential PNG file to determine if it is, in fact, a PNG file
    WinExeFileHeaderMap
    Map to easily parse the header of standard Windows Executable files (.exe, .dll, etc).
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.DOSHeaderMap
    Map to parse the "DOS Header" section of the executable file header.
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap
    Map to parse the "PE Header" section of the executable file header.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BmpHeaderMap.ColorSpaceType
    Possible values for the ColorSpace field in the BITMAPV4HEADER
    BmpHeaderMap.CompressionType
    Possible values for the Compression field in the BITMAPINFOHEADER
    BmpHeaderMap.DIBHeaderSize
    The Size field in the DIB Header determines what data will follow it BITMAPV3INFOHEADER - BITMAPV5INFOHEADER simply expand upon the previous header.
    BmpHeaderMap.RenderingIntent
    Possible values for the Intent field in the BITMAPV5HEADER
    PngFileMap.ColorTypeEnum
    Enum to represent the possible values of the ColorType field in the "IHDR" chunk.
    PngFileMap.MonthEnum
    Enum to parse the Month field in "tIME" chunk.
    PngFileMap.SRGBRenderingIntent
    Enum to represent the possible values of the RenderingIntent field of the "sRGB" chunk
    PngFileMap.UnitSpecifierEnum
    Enum to represent the possible values of the UnitSpecifier field in the "pHYs" chunk
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.MachineId
    Enum to represent the various possible values in the Machine variable in COFFHeaderMap
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEOptionalHeaderMagic
    Enum to represent the various possible values in the Magic variable in PEOptionalHeader
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.SubsystemId
    Enum to represent the various possible values in the Subsystem variable in PEOptionalHeader
